data.description: ** VA Assumable Rate of 2.62% ** This 5 bedroom 3 bath home is full of functional living space.  This home features a spacious, welcoming foyer that lets in an abundance of natural light.   The foyer connects to the dining room which then leads to the kitchen. The kitchen is full of usable space and features granite countertops, with stainless steel appliances.  The main living area of the home has luxury wood look vinyl for easy maintenance.  Downstairs features a guest bedroom and  separate full bathroom.  The upstairs owner's suite is roomy and the private bath offers granite countertops, double vanity, garden tub with tile and walk in shower.  Three other bedrooms and bathroom are located upstairs off of the spacious landing area.  The backyard offers plenty of room and includes a storage building.
